{"word":"G3718 - ὀρθοτομέω - orthotoméō - or-thot-om-eh'-o - Rightly divide","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὀρθοτομέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">orthotoméō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">or-thot-om-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Rightly divide</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நிதானமாய்ப்பகு"},{"paragraph":"1. to cut straight"},{"paragraph":"2. dropping the idea of cutting, to make straight and smooth"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G3717 - ὀρθός - orthós - or-thos'/3717\">G3717</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G5114 - τομώτερος - tomṓteros - tom-o'-ter-os/5114\">G5114</a>; to <i>make</i> a <i>straight cut</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>dissect</i> (<i>expound</i>) <i>correctly</i> (the divine message): - rightly divide.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1357/1357\">G1357</a>, <a href=\"#/G1882/1882\">G1882</a>, <a href=\"#/G2699/2699\">G2699</a>, <a href=\"#/G3716/3716\">G3716</a>, <a href=\"#/G3717/3717\">G3717</a>, <a href=\"#/G3718/3718\">G3718</a>, <a href=\"#/G3719/3719\">G3719</a>, <a href=\"#/G3720/3720\">G3720</a>, <a href=\"#/G3721/3721\">G3721</a>, <a href=\"#/G3722/3722\">G3722</a>, <a href=\"#/G3723/3723\">G3723</a>, <a href=\"#/G663/663\">G663</a>, <a href=\"#/G664/664\">G664</a>"}]}